<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7a278e3c-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s7401"><num value="7401">§ 7401.</num><heading> Purpose</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The purpose of this chapter is to implement the Agreement on Port State Measures to Prevent, Deter and Eliminate Illegal, Unreported and Unregulated Fishing.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7a278e3d-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/114/81/tIII/s302">Pub. L. 114–81, title III, § 302</ref>, <date date="2015-11-05">Nov. 5, 2015</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/129/664">129 Stat. 664</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id7a278e3e-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="id7a278e3f-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="shortTitle" id="id7a278e40-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Short Title</heading><p><ref href="/us/pl/114/81/tIII/s301">Pub. L. 114–81, title III, § 301</ref>, <date date="2015-11-05">Nov. 5, 2015</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/129/664">129 Stat. 664</ref>, provided that: <quotedContent origin="/us/pl/114/81/tIII/s301">“This title [enacting this chapter] may be cited as the ‘Port State Measures Agreement Act of 2015’.”</quotedContent>
</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
